scene.message:
Brown: That was my first time{nl}
ever in a jail cell!{waitkey}{clearbox}I was a little nervous, but{nl}
looking back, it was pretty{nl}
fun!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Better safe than{nl}
sorry!{wait_fr:37} ...as Yamaoka{nl}
used to often say.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: I've got plenty I want{nl}
to say to Kandori. That guy,{nl}
above all, I won't forgive.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: We're going to the{nl}
abandoned factory, yes? I'd{nl}
never paid a place like that{nl}
any mind before...{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: We must go after{nl}
Mr. Kandori soon...{wait_fr:32}{nl}
We can't just leave him be!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Yeah, that's right.{nl}
We're storming SEBEC, after{nl}
all. We oughta at least bring{nl}
some medicine!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: We've gotta chase down{nl}
Kandori...{wait_fr:21} there's no telling{nl}
what he'll do!{waitkey}{ret}

Shopkeeper: Yes, welcome!{waitkey}{clearbox}Hey, have you met Tamaki?{nl}
I'm just so worried about{nl}
whether she's safe...{waitkey}I couldn't care less about{nl}
my own son, mind you!{nl}
...Hm? Oh, medicine? Right.{waitkey}{ret}

Shopkeeper: Oh? If it's{nl}
medicine you want, it's{nl}
over here!{waitkey}{ret}
